      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "Engineered in Australia",
        "heading": "Built for Aussie Roads. Proven on the Track.",
        "paragraph": "<p>Every component we design starts with one question: will it survive Australian conditions? From coastal salt air to outback heat, our parts are engineered to withstand the extremes — not just look good in a catalogue photo.</p><p>We don't sign off on a product until fitment is perfect and finish meets our own exacting standards. Factory-direct pricing means you get premium quality without the premium markup.</p>",
